Title: Super-Yangian Y(gl(1|1)) and Its Oscillator Realization

Authors: G.X. Ju, J.F. Cai, H.Y. Guo, K. Wu and S.K. Wang

Comments: 7 pages, latex, no figures, to appaer in the International Workshop

on Frontiers in Quantum Field Theory,Urumqi,11-18,Augast,1996Journal-ref: J.Phys. A30 (1997) 6155-6161

